import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Button, Dropdown, Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import App from '../App'

export default function AppMenu() {
    return (
        <Menu size='large'>

            <Menu.Item>
                <Button primary>Login</Button>
            </Menu.Item>
            </Menu.Menu>

}
